{"tid":2314976,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京公安智能鐵馬 配備鏡頭主動拍攝違法情況","createTime":"2020-12-07T02:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T02:07:41.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"14ac755ca969f220662140fa7e35a10400298c60","tid":2314976,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:06:20.000Z","msg":"報導指這批巡邏電單車擁有極高智能化程度，除了安裝可視化預警裝置，亦配備車載 T-BOX 設備，能夠主動識別違法交通行為的智能鏡頭。公安在駕駛電單車巡邏時，鏡頭會自主搜索違反交通法的行為，一旦確認車輛違法，就會自動拍攝相關的違法畫面，用於後續檢控和處分。鏡頭的另一用處是在抵達事故現場後，以直播方式將畫面傳送到指揮中心；就算電單車只是停在路邊，鏡頭仍然會主動搜索、識別、記錄違規的車輛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/07/beijing-police-smart-motorcycle/life-tech/auto/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2Fbeijing-police-smart-motorcycle%2Flife-tech%2Fauto%2F&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2nHr90zhVRml9IH8Z62du0k%3D&h=706e997b\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/07/beijing-police-smart-motorcycle/life-tech/auto/</a>"},{"pid":"5ebcdd5697f6c8682f6da2cdd3829a2b4261c657","tid":2314976,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/15m5ZRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F15m5ZRY.jpg&h=2e0a5202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越來越似 GAME 入面D 高科技邪惡國家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d04d41dfa7483153e6fec8fb541e1ccca4ac7ae","tid":2314976,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/819ijTWp9JL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F819ijTWp9JL.jpg&h=14033dc1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}